                <h2>Contributing</h2>
                <p>If you're new to the workflow, follow these steps to get started:</p>
                <ul>
                    <md-block>
                    - step 1: clone the Nexus repository
                    - step 3: download <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bbedit/id404009241?mt=12">*BBEdit*</a> for mac or VS-Code for windows.
                    - step 3: clone the <a href="https://github.com/JohnTeBrown/app-server">*app server*</a> developer archive from our Github
                    - step 4: open app server and navigate to the *www* directory
                    - step 5: drag **all** of the files and folders from the Nexus repo clone into the *www* directory
                    - step 6: run ```php server.php -7``` in the main app-server directory to start the php server
                    </md-block>
                </ul>
