                <h2>Common Questions</h2>
                <p>Here are some frequently asked questions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <md-block>
                    - why are .php pages not displaying content? => *the web-server must be started, if your using a packaged version of Nexus make a Github issue if this is a issue.*
                    
                    - why is Nexus failing to failing to build? => *the Nexus on the GitHub repository has countermeasures to prevent unauthorized packaging and tampering, you must make a pull-request to have your changes packaged.*
                    </md-block>
                </ul>
		    
